### Shipments are delegated to the bundled LogisticsService CAP app
### (port 4455). Same pattern as delegating to a public OData service —
### the federation plugin does not care whether the target is remote
### SaaS or an internal CAP service.
GET http://localhost:4005/odata/v4/sales-intel/Shipments?$top=5

### Filter by Northwind OrderID — a plain integer field in the shipment
GET http://localhost:4005/odata/v4/sales-intel/Shipments?$filter=orderId eq 10248

### Delegated expand: to-many tracking events nested on the shipment
GET http://localhost:4005/odata/v4/sales-intel/Shipments?$top=2&$expand=events($orderby=timestamp desc;$top=3)

### Only exceptional shipments
GET http://localhost:4005/odata/v4/sales-intel/Shipments?$filter=status eq 'exception'
